(******************************************************* TLA+ Specification ***  *)   (* Sat Oct31 PDT209 ** )    *     (      This specifies a system that alternately performs two actions, which are A_O andA _I. It uses avariable v whose valuealternates between Oand I , performing anAction of type AI whenv changes from  IO to II . We let thevariable x representthe partof th estate changed by thesections: Initiallyx is assumedto haveacorrect initialvalue, and XAct(i)isassumedtor epresentachangingofthe value oxfrom itsinitialvaluetoitsnext v aluerepresent anA_I actionfor i=0 , 1 . *)
